[SkillPath "competitive_bidding/lebensohl"]
[Student "S"]
{Partner's direct cue-bid is the lebensohl equivalent of Stayman, but with no \D stopper.

With 4 cards in both Majors you bid 3\H.

Partner then bids 4\H which you pass.}

[Event ""]
[Site ""]
[Date ""]
