[Student "S"]
{Partner's 2NT bid is lebensohl, asking you to bid 3\C. You bid 3\C. Partner says 3\H.

How about . . . . pass? Partner just signed off with this sequence. He couldn't bid 3\H directly, that would have been a game-force.}

